It is located in the heartland of the Masovian Plain , and its average elevation is 100 metres -LRB- 330 ft -RRB- above sea level .
The highest point on the left side of the city lies at a height of 115.7 metres -LRB- 379.6 ft -RRB- -LRB- `` Redutowa '' bus depot , district of Wola -RRB- , on the right side -- 122.1 metres -LRB- 400.6 ft -RRB- -LRB- `` Groszówka '' estate , district of Wesoła , by the eastern border -RRB- .
