It goes through the city and plays an important role as a landmark .
The pattern of the Vistula terraces is asymmetrical .
They consist of still quite natural streams and lakes as well as the pattern of drainage ditches .
The right side of Warsaw has a different pattern of geomorphological forms .
Aeolian sand with a number of dunes parted by peat swamps or small ponds cover the highest terrace .
Most of the historical buildings were thoroughly reconstructed .
Among the first structures of the early baroque the most important are St. Hyacinth 's Church -LRB- 1603 -- 1639 -RRB- and Sigismund 's Column -LRB- 1644 -RRB- .
The economic growth during the first years of Congress Poland caused a rapid rise architecture .
The Neoclassical revival affected all aspects of architecture , the most notable are the Great Theater -LRB- 1825 -- 1833 -RRB- and buildings located at Bank Square -LRB- 1825 -- 1828 -RRB- .
Some 19th-century buildings in the Praga district -LRB- the Vistula 's right bank -RRB- have been restored although many have been poorly maintained .
The oldest park in Praga , the Praga Park , was established in 1865 -- 1871 and designed by Jan Dobrowolski .
The flora of the city may be considered very rich in species .
Bielany Forest nature reserve is connected with Kampinos Forest .
It is home to rich fauna and flora .
Within the forest there are three cycling and walking trails .
During the first years after the war , the population growth was c. 6 % , so shortly the city started to suffer from the lack of flats and of areas for new houses .
Eight years later , in 1909 , there were 281,754 Jews -LRB- 36.9 % -RRB- , 18,189 Protestants -LRB- 2.4 % -RRB- and 2,818 Mariavites -LRB- 0.4 % -RRB- .
This led to construction of hundreds of places of religious worship in all parts of the town .
After the war , the new communist authorities of Poland discouraged church construction and only a small number were rebuilt .
A city is also a commune -- but with the city charter .
Both cities and communes are governed by a mayor -- but in the communes the mayor is vogt -LRB- wójt in Polish -RRB- , however in the cities -- burmistrz .
An example of such entitlement is a car registration : a gmina can not register cars , this is a powiat 's task -LRB- i.e. a registration number depends on what powiat a car had been registered , not gmina -RRB- .
