Jamukha horrified people greatly and harmed his image by boiling seventy young male captives alive in cauldrons , alienating many of his potential followers and eliciting sympathy for Temüjin .
The life of Temüjin for the next ten years is very unclear , as historical records are mostly silent on that period .
