He left a commander and number of troops in China , designated his successors to be his family members and likely appointed Ögedei to be his immediate successor and then went out to Khwarezmia .
His son Jochi led the first division into the northeast of Khwarezmia .
The Shah 's army was split by diverse internecine feuds and by the Shah 's decision to divide his army into small groups concentrated in various cities .
The Shah died under mysterious circumstances on a small island within his empire .
The Mongols ' conquest , even by their own standards , was brutal .
