The name Eleventh is still used for this incarnation ; the same episode depicts the prophesied `` Fall of the Eleventh '' which had been trailed throughout the series .
In the 1967 serial , Tomb of the Cybermen , when Victoria Waterfield doubts the Doctor can remember his family because of , `` being so ancient '' , the Doctor says that he can when he really wants to -- `` The rest of the time they sleep in my mind '' .
