Controversy over the actual meaning of the word Kenya notwithstanding , it is clear that the mountain 's name became widely accepted , pars pro toto , as the name of the country .
A significant population of other wild animals , reptiles and birds can be found in the national parks and game reserves in the country .
This Serengeti Migration of the wildebeest is a curious spectacle listed among the 10 Natural Wonders of Africa .
