Coconuts , pineapples , cashew nuts , cotton , sugarcane , sisal , and corn are grown in the lower-lying areas .
Poor roads , an inadequate railway network , under-used water transport and expensive air transport have isolated mostly arid and semi-arid areas and farmers in other regions often leave food to rot in the fields because they can not access markets .
There is a cement production industry .
-LSB- citation needed -RSB- Kenya has an oil refinery that processes imported crude petroleum into petroleum products , mainly for the domestic market .
